# LITE shaders version 4.7.3

Changelog:

- Thanks to tasxatzial for beta testing this version.

# OVERVIEW:
- This version fixes bugs and adjusts some features.

# INHERITED from MakeUp 9.3h:
- Much of the broken compatibility with previous versions of Minecraft (from 1.12 onward) has been fixed.
- Fixed an issue that made the beacon beam invisible from certain distances or angles when using Distant Horizons.

# General changes:
- MAX stars on overworld are disabled on old versions of Minecraft. (below 1.16.4)
- Reduced brightness of MAX stars.

# Bugfixes:
- Fixed weird lighting when enabling simpler exposure.
- Fixed too bright scene when using simpler exposure + LITE Vanilla color scheme.
- Fixed sky flicker when exiting pale garden or any gray sky biome.

Version code: LT473

Based in MakeUp Ultrafast 9.3e

Olá de Entokito :) 